summary: Complete summary of build status and UI testing for the Flutter Partner App. Documents successful resolution of all build issues, Windows release build completion with zero errors, automated UI test execution with 8 screenshots, comprehensive manual testing checklist covering 14 feature areas, test scripts for both automated and manual testing, and detailed implementation status of all features including authentication, dashboard, user management (hotspot/email), plan configuration, active sessions, revenue tracking, and worker management. Includes quick start guide, test credentials, and recommendations for next steps.
